title: Person of Interest 1x22 Because i built it
author: George Finch
comment: After 7 years I still keep coming to this video and I get goosebumps every time... One of the best shows of all times...
every time finch said:"I BUILD IT", i feel Goosebumps!
I like the face the guy makes when he just realized he was standing before the father of a god
I love this show so much, and THESE scenes where mortals find out about gods are the BEST. I really ought to watch it a third time. Thank the Machine for Netflix.
They cut at the wrong moment!! Should have included ALICIA's reaction! THAT WAS THE WHOLE POINT!
